        <body>
            <div>
               
	<pb facs="liv_001172_0001" n="0001"/>
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>50 Albemarle <choice><abbr>St.</abbr><expan>Street</expan></choice></placeName> <add place="above" rend="gray" hand="#U">14</add>
<lb/><space extent="3" unit="chars"/><date when="1858-01-08">8<hi rend="sup underline">th</hi> January
<lb/><space extent="6" unit="chars"/>1858</date></p><!-- Change line info as appropriate -->
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><add hand="#U" rend="gray small"><add place="marginleft">To</add> <persName>Alexander Macmillan</persName>
<lb/><space extent="2" unit="chars"/>The founder of the <orgName>Publishing
<lb/><space extent="1" unit="words"/>House of Macmillan</orgName></add></p>
<lb/>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent"><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>My Dear Sir</p><!-- Change line info as appropriate -->
<lb/><p><space extent="8" unit="chars"/>I am really quite
<lb/>ashamed to find that so much
<lb/>time has glided away since
<lb/>I received your most kind 
<lb/>and liberal present of books 
<lb/>and no acknowledgement 
<lb/>been made, I <choice><sic>dont</sic><corr>don't</corr></choice> stand
<lb/>lionizing well you see
<lb/>it makes me forget
                
	<pb facs="liv_001172_0002" n="0002"/>
<lb/>my best friends and I suppose 
<lb/>some of them will be saying
<lb/>I have "forgotten myself."
<lb/>So many things have occupied
<lb/>my attention of late that
<lb/>time speeds on more swiftly
<lb/>than ever it did. Indeed
<lb/>one has scarcely time to
<lb/>think in this whirl and
<lb/>glad I shall be if I again
<lb/>get a little time in <placeName><bloc>Africa</bloc></placeName>
<lb/>to think. I beg you will
<lb/>forgive my long silence
<lb/>I went down to <placeName><country>Scotland</country></placeName>
                
	<pb facs="liv_001172_0003" n="0003"/>
<lb/>to spend Christmas and New 
<lb/><choice><orig>yearsday</orig><reg>Year's Day</reg></choice> and have neglected 
<lb/>many duties in consequence
<lb/>none of which I regret more
<lb/>than that <add place="below">^</add> <add place="above">which made me</add> <del type="strikethrough">of</del> appear<del type="strikethrough">ing</del> wanting
<lb/>in gratitude to you for your 
<lb/>liberality. I return you my
<lb/>warmest thanks for the
<lb/>books and feel most
<lb/>grateful for the kind
<lb/>sentences which <w>accom<supplied>-</supplied>
<lb break="no"/>-panied</w> them. May our
<lb/>Heavenly Father abundantly
<lb/>reward you for all your
<lb/>kindly feelings.</p>
    
    <pb facs="liv_001172_0004" n="0004"/>
<lb/><p>Please present my
<lb/>kindest salutations to your
<lb/>family nephews for
<lb/>I suppose your brother's
<lb/>children stay with you</p>
<lb/><p><space extent="4" unit="chars"/>Hoping you are
<lb/>of a forgiving dispostion</p>
<lb/><closer><salute><space extent="2" unit="chars"/>I am truly &amp; gratefully
<lb/><space extent="4" unit="chars"/>yours</salute>
<lb/><space extent="4" unit="chars"/><signed><persName>David Livingstone</persName></signed></closer>


            </div>
